istory: Municipal Amalgamations (2015) | publisher=The Manitoba Historical Society | date=December 1, 2014 | accessdate=January 2, 2015}}</ref>\n\nThe former RM surrounds the [[Virden, Manitoba|Town of Virden]].\n\n== Communities ==\n* [[Hargrave, Manitoba|Hargrave]]\n* [[Harmsworth, Manitoba|Harmsworth]]\n* [[Kirkella, Manitoba|Kirkella]]\n* [[Kola, Manitoba|Kola]]\n* [[Maples, Manitoba|Maples]]\n* [[Two Creeks, Manitoba|Two Creeks]]\n\n== Reeves ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Name\n! In Office\n|-\n| [[Adam Gerrond McDougall]]\n| 1884\u20131887\n|-\n| [[James Frame|James Findlay Frame]]\n| 1888\u20131891\n|-\n| William M. Cushing\n| 1892\n|-\n| [[Watson Montgomery Crosby]]\n| 1893\u20131896\n|-\n| George A. Freeman\n| 1897\u20131899\n|-\n| John Joslin\n| 1900\u20131902\n|-\n| Amos Odell\n| 1903\u20131904\n|-\n| Christopher Stinson\n| 1905\u20131907\n|-\n| Charles E. Ivens\n| 1908\u20131943\n|-\n| Harvey Cecil Odell\n| 1944\u20131967\n|-\n| Maxwell James Edgar\n| 1968\u20131983\n|-\n| Keith Kinnaird\n| 1984\u20131992\n|-\n| Alex Gabrielle\n| 1993\u20131997\n|-\n| Jim Penner\n| 1998\u20132001\n|-\n| Vince Heaman\n| 2002\u20132010\n|-\n| Richard Murphy\n| November 9, 2010 \u2013 August 9, 2011\n|-\n| Don Neufeld\n| Incumbent\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|http://www.rmofwallace.com/}}\n* [http://www.mhs.mb.ca/docs/municipalities/wallace.shtml ''Manitoba Municipalities: Rural Municipality of Wallace'']\n* [http://geodepot.statcan.ca/GeoSearch2006/GeoSearch2006.jsp?resolution=H&lang=E&otherLang=F&census=Yes&DisplayData=Yes&NewImage=yes&layer=csd&IdentName=Wallace%20(RM)&IdentUID=4606028 ''Map of Wallace R.M. at Statcan'']\n\n{{MBDivision6}}\n{{Manitoba|rural=yes}}\n\n{{Manitoba-geo-stub}}\n\n{{coord|49|55|51|N|101|09|38|W|scale:500000|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Former rural municipalities in Manitoba|Wallace]]\n[[Category:Populated places disestablished in 2015]]\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label