{"title_page": "Rural Municipality of Saskatchewan", "text_new": "The '''Rural Municipality of Saskatchewan''' is a former [[rural municipality]] (RM) in the [[Canada|Canadian]] [[Provinces and territories of Canada|province]] of Manitoba. It was originally incorporated as a rural municipality on December 22, 1883.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mhs.mb.ca/docs/municipalities/rural.shtml|title=Manitoba\u2019s Municipal History: Rural Municipalities and Local Government Districts|publisher=The Manitoba Historical Society|date=September 21, 2014|accessdate=January 2, 2015}}</ref> It ceased on January 1, 2015 as a result of its [[Manitoba municipal amalgamations, 2015|provincially mandated]] [[Merger (politics)|amalgamation]] with the [[Rural Municipality of Blanshard|RM of Blanshard]] and the [[Rapid City, Manitoba|Town of Rapid City]] to form the [[Rural Municipality of Oakview]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mhs.mb.ca/docs/municipalities/amalgamations.shtml|title=Manitoba\u2019s Municipal History: Municipal Amalgamations (2015)|publisher=The Manitoba Historical Society|date=December 1, 2014|accessdate=January 2, 2015}}</ref>\n\n== Communities ==\n* Basswood\n* Riverdale\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://geodepot.statcan.ca/GeoSearch2006/GeoSearch2006.jsp?resolution=H&lang=E&otherLang=F&census=Yes&DisplayData=Yes&NewImage=yes&layer=csd&IdentName=Saskatchewan%20(RM)&IdentUID=4615027 Map of Saskatchewan R.M. at Statcan]\n\n{{MBDivision15}}\n{{Manitoba|rural=yes}}\n{{coord|50|11|47|N|100|04|59|W|scale:250000|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Former rural municipalities in Manitoba|Saskatchewan]]\n[[Category:Populated places disestablished in 2015]]\n[[Category:2015 disestablishments in Manitoba]]\n{{Manitoba-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "The '''Rural Municipality of Saskatchewan''' is a former [[rural municipality]] (RM) in the [[Canada|Canadian]] [[Provinces and territories of Canada|province]] of Manitoba. It was originally incorporated as a rural municipality on December 22, 1883.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mhs.mb.ca/docs/municipalities/rural.shtml|title=Manitoba\u2019s Municipal History: Rural Municipalities and Local Government Districts|publisher=The Manitoba Historical Society|date=September 21, 2014|accessdate=January 2, 2015}}</ref> It ceased on January 1, 2015 as a result of its [[Manitoba municipal amalgamations, 2015|provincially mandated]] [[Merger (politics)|amalgamation]] with the [[Rural Municipality of Blanshard|RM of Blanshard]] and the [[Rapid City, Manitoba|Town of Rapid City]] to form the [[Rural Municipality of Oakview]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mhs.mb.ca/docs/municipalities/amalgamations.shtml|title=Manitoba\u2019s Municipal History: Municipal Amalgamations (2015)|publisher=The Manitoba Historical Society|date=December 1, 2014|accessdate=January 2, 2015}}</ref>\n\n== Communities ==\n* Basswood\n* Riverdale\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://geodepot.statcan.ca/GeoSearch2006/GeoSearch2006.jsp?resolution=H&lang=E&otherLang=F&census=Yes&DisplayData=Yes&NewImage=yes&layer=csd&IdentName=Saskatchewan%20(RM)&IdentUID=4615027 Map of Saskatchewan R.M. at Statcan]\n\n{{MBDivision15}}\n{{Manitoba|rural=yes}}\n{{coord|50|11|47|N|100|04|59|W|scale:250000|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Former rural municipalities in Manitoba|Saskatchewan]]\n[[Category:Populated places disestablished in 2015]]\n\n{{Manitoba-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "Copying fromCategory:Populated places disestablished in 2015toCategory:2015 disestablishments in ManitobausingCat-a-lot", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rural_Municipality_of_Saskatchewan"}
